description:
Fixed A LOT of problems in this tab:
- First of all, the timing issues have been resolved. The crummy 1/4 bar has been removed and the uptempo riff (heard at 1:43) and following verses were corrected such that the snare lands on beats 2 and 4.
- To help in fixing the timing issues, much of the song was changed into eighth notes rather than sixteenth notes.
- Reworked the intro slow down.
- Made better section titles.
- Drums rewritten.
- Improved the vocal tracks, but there's still some small errors in pitch and rhythm.

Things that still need looking into:
- Many of the drum parts do not match the actual song.
- Small errors in pitch and rhythm in the vocal track throughout the entire song.
title: Fear Of The Dark
